title: Jenn-Air® Connected Refrigerator | Jenn-Air
description: Refreshing innovation, purposeful design, and unparalleled convenience – all available in the palm of your hand. Similar to our Jenn-Air® connected wall ovens, the latest Jenn-Air® counter-depth French door refrigerator features wireless connectivity and a fully functioning application for IOS and Android devices. In addition to a range of Smart Features, from remote monitoring to maintenance reminders, our connected refrigerator offers a generous capacity and spacious interior. And with food preservation features like our FreshFlow™ Air Filter, TwinFresh™ Climate Control System, Humidiseal™ Crisper Drawers, and more, you can be sure to enjoy fresh ingredients in all your favorite recipes.
